listings.comment: The experience of working with Hubspot Techie was disappointing. The project faced numerous delays, as he missed every deadline and didn’t fully meet the requirements outlined in the original brief. Despite no changes to the scope, he requested additional payment, which added to the frustration. To top it off, a critical email sent to a large group failed to work as intended, which was a major letdown. While he did eventually deliver, the overall process was far from satisfactory.

Hubspot Techie truly IMPRESSED with their impeccable attention to detail and professionalism in website development. Their code expertise and POLITE demeanor made collaboration seamless, and they consistently went above and beyond expectations. Highly recommend their services! 🙌

Hubspot Techie is an outstanding website developer! His PROFESSIONALISM and code expertise shine through in every project, and his quick responsiveness and polite communication make him a joy to work with. Consistently delivering top-quality results—HIGHLY recommended! 👍

Working with Hubspot Techie was a pleasure! The professionalism and attention to detail in the website development were impressive; everything was executed flawlessly. Their proactive communication and timely delivery made the process SMOOTH and efficient. 👏

First phase of the project is just finished. Enjoyed working together with Hubspot_Techie. 

Looking forward to the next phase and finalising the project!
